i want u to build this website using vite react typscript for the frontend node and express and mongo db for the backend and database PRODUCT REQUIREMENTS DOCUMENT (PRD)
Project Title

Association of Cybersecurity Practitioners (ACSP) – Official Website & Membership Platform

1. Introduction
1.1 Purpose

This document defines the functional and non-functional requirements for designing and developing the official website and membership platform of the Association of Cybersecurity Practitioners (ACSP).

The platform will serve as:

The official digital presence of ACSP

A membership registration and verification system

A knowledge-sharing and professional networking hub

A dynamic content management system for conferences, events, blogs, and announcements

1.2 Goals & Objectives

Establish a credible, secure, and modern online identity

Enable member registration, verification, and engagement

Provide a controlled forum accessible only to verified members

Allow administrators full control over all website content

Promote events, conferences, research, and innovation

Reflect ACSP’s professional cybersecurity brand

2. Branding & Design System
2.1 Brand Identity (Derived from Poster)

Primary Colors (from poster):

Deep Blue – Authority, trust, technology

Cyber Green – Security, innovation, growth

White – Cleanliness, professionalism, clarity

These colors must be implemented as theme variables, not hardcoded.

Suggested Palette (Adjustable)

Primary Blue: #0A1A4A

Accent Blue: #0D47A1

Primary Green: #1DB954

Accent Green: #00E676

White: #FFFFFF

Neutral Gray: #F5F7FA

2.2 UI/UX Principles

Clean, modern, cyber-themed design

Professional typography (e.g., Inter, Poppins, Roboto)

Fully responsive (mobile, tablet, desktop)

Accessible (WCAG considerations)

Clear call-to-action (CTA) buttons

3. User Roles & Permissions
3.1 Public Users (Unregistered)

View homepage

View events & conferences

Read blogs & announcements

View services & gallery

Contact ACSP

Cannot post, comment, or join forums

3.2 Registered Members (Unverified)

Register account

Verify email via OTP/token

Login

Complete profile:

Upload passport photo

Upload ID card

Fill professional information

Cannot access forums until verified

3.3 Verified Members

Access members-only dashboard

Join and post in forums

Comment and reply to discussions

View verified-only announcements

Connect with other members

3.4 Admin

Full system control

Verify or reject members

Manage website content

Manage forums and posts

Manage events, blogs, announcements

Moderate users

Upload and manage media

