5. Authentication & Membership System
5.1 Registration

Fields:

Full Name

Email Address

Password

Security:

Password hashing (bcrypt)

Email uniqueness

5.2 Email Verification

OTP or token sent to email

Token expiration

Verified status required before login access

5.3 Member Profile Completion (Post-Login)

Required:

Passport photograph

ID card upload

Phone number

Institution / Organization

Area of specialization

Short bio

Status:

Pending verification

Verified

Rejected

5.4 Admin Verification

View submitted documents

Approve or reject

Optional rejection reason

Email notification to member

6. Member Dashboard
Features

Profile status (Pending / Verified)

Edit profile

Forum access (if verified)

Notifications

Account settings

7. Admin Dashboard
Content Management

Pages

Carousel slides

Announcements

Events

Blogs

Gallery

User Management

View members

Verify / reject

Suspend users

Forum Moderation

Delete posts

Lock threads

Ban users

